snippet.textDisplay:
'Animes da and pantho da' ❤️
Probably one of the most energetic duo in the bangla music industry. The more you listen to this song the more you fall in love with them! Body language, expression with perfect voice!
Animes da has a very addictive and powerful voice and pantho da has that old school melody vibe when he sings "দোল দোল দোলনি,রাঙা মাথায় চিরুনি!"
Loved it ❤️
Looking forward to more amazing works ❤️
